[6] Evacuations, Myanmar
Date: 2 Feb 2020
Source: Reuters [edited]
https://news.mb.com.ph/2020/02/02/myanmar-students-flown-home-from-coronavirus-stricken-wuhan/


Dozens of Myanmar students were evacuated from the coronavirus-stricken Chinese city of Wuhan early Sun 2 Feb 2020, government officials said, the latest foreign nationals to be flown home from the region.

